crsf.description: Scans for cross-origin resource sharing misconfigurations

ssrf.description: Scans for misconfigurations leading to SSRF

xss.description: Scans for reflections and unsanitized content

sqli.description: Scans for unsanitized inputs and params

secrets.description: Scans for hardcoded api keys on the client source

crawler.description: Crawls the websites to uncover more vectors of attack

fuzz.description: Fuzzes the website to uncover hidden files/directories

idor.description: Scans for IDOR vulns where access controls can be bypassed by manipulating object identifiers

nmap.description: Port scans a target to look for open ports and running services

subdomain_search.description: Search for subdomains on the target

pdf.description: Converts any specified file into a .pdf
